  <brief_title>Endotracheal Intubation Using Bonfils Fibrescope Without Neuromuscular Blockade</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparing Intubating Conditions and Hemodynamic Changes Between Macintosh Laryngoscopy and Bonfils Fibrescope During Endotracheal Intubation Without Neuromuscular Blockade</official_title>
